# ========================================
# 🚀 RENDER DEPLOYMENT - KEEP-ALIVE SYSTEM
# ========================================
# CRITICAL: To prevent Render free instance spin-down (50+ second delays):
# 1. Set BACKEND_URL to your Render backend URL
# 2. Set NODE_ENV=production
# 3. The system will automatically self-ping every 14 minutes
# 4. No external cron-job.org service needed!
# 
# Example: BACKEND_URL=https://your-app-name.onrender.com
# ========================================

